submissions.author: Gollyyy#5024
submissions.text: Hello its me Golly , I just wanna to say exactly this day ,one year ago I showed you guys my art for the first time and the response was so great I keep showing and showing .Now ,a year have gone by and it was such a wild ride for me , thanks to you guys I managed to get my own pc for the first time in my life and Vr and a table and a drawing tablet, my life just changed after that . From the bottom of my heart I want to say thank you so much and I love everyone,all the love and support I appreciate all of it , I hope my silly drawings repay some of it . I hope your (Rob) community keep growing and have even more beautiful memories in the future. Thank you for changing this lil rice farmer life and please do have a lovely day ~Golly ( ps welcome back Rob, we all missed you a lot ,now back to work lump head)
